FireStrike gleared at him with fire in his eyes.  "All I ever ehar 
from you is, ' Yes master, orders master. ' BE YOUR OWN BOT PIT 
DAMNIT"  He let his sword drop to his side. "I just don't want you to 
be owned by Megatron or anyone else.  I have been awoken from his 
control over me.  We cannot be scared of him. WE are strong, and must 
not let him be our master.  We will not fight for him but for the 
cause, but never again will he be our master.
Do you understand?"
